<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢ - <span class="c2">(٢٤١٢)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5609">وَابْنُ رُمْحٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ </a>. <span class="c2">(ح)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">ابْنُ الْمُثَنَّى </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4085">عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ </a>- كِلَاهُمَا عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>